item.title: I recently obtained the game i was wanting to steel
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

Your problem: goto is a reserved keyword in java. It has yet to serve a purpose, and thus when the compile reaches a goto statement, it freaks out and gives you all thsoe errors. basically, you could comment out the goto’s and the _L6 and shit, and it should work fine.
